# EmotiLive: Real-Time Student Engagement Monitoring System

EmotiLive is an advanced AI-based system designed to monitor and analyze student engagement and emotional behavior in real time during classroom sessions. It combines computer vision, deep learning, and video enhancement technologies to support educators with live feedback on student attentiveness and emotions.

